---
title: Sticky Double Beef Meatballs & Jasmine Rice with Soy Garlic Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet chilli and oyster sauce has to be our new favourite flavour combo and it’s even better turned into a glaze and slathered all over savoury beef meatballs. Don’t let that extra sauce go to waste - soak it up with jasmine rice and spoon it over the garlicky veggies to max out on those delicious flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2acc3a27a53fcaa21ea0c-d3c9fa0e.jpeg
